       Returns  the  information about setEndCapMode parameters in the Innovus
       log file and in the Innovus console. Returns the following information:

              * Parameter name

              * Current value

              * Type (Boolean, string, and so on)

              * Source of current value (default, user)

       If you do not specify a parameter, the software displays values for all
       of the setEndCapMode mode parameters.

